    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont mean like a nap or a vacation. i mean like... what if the \"rest\" isnt coming back? like, is it ever actually okay to just give up on everything for good? people always say it gets better but what if it doesnt?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
